  "title": "Spicy Crunchy Egyptian Rest-Meat Tagine",
  "description": "A lacto-vegetarian-friendly, spicy and crunchy Egyptian dish perfect for a date night. This tagine is made with rest-meat and light rum for a unique flavor.",
